# SFPTotal-Protocol
Description of the command protocol for programmers SFPTotal


#Read and write
rXYYAABBCC (RXYYAABBCC)
Command for reading memory of transceiver.

r1A000007F
Read 128 byte(s) Table 0xA0 from 0x00
